  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, it is equally important to pay attention to users employing AI systems in contexts of vulnerability, such as in education.",
    "While the use of GPAIS in educational settings holds promising applications, it also imposes changes that do not always benefit the involved users.",
    "For instance, it might compel us to modify teaching and testing methods, possibly abandoning wellestablished and effective practices.",
    "Taking stock, we have seen how keeping in mind a multi-component analysis of risk puts us in a better position to cope with AI-related risks emerging from the use of AI experimental technologies and general-purpose systems.",
    "Besides being increasingly popular, LLMs are a perfect example of such technologies."
  ],
